summarizedActivitiesExport.name: Charlotte Running
summarizedActivitiesExport.description: Around mile 3-4.5 the inside of my right ankle and right hip flexor were both bothering me but it got better after that. Elevation is definitely a game changer. I felt better towards the end when I tried to bounce off the ground at impact - meaning my steps werent as heavy. Specifically, the bouncing feeling helped on vertical ascents.

summarizedActivitiesExport.name: Treadmill Running
summarizedActivitiesExport.description: Body felt good, but conditioning felt worse than my last 3 mile run.
